id: pm-2t78
title: Sync package JS runtimes to public SDK surface
description: "The first-party package TypeScript runtimes import runtime primitives from the public SDK barrel, but the shipped JavaScript runtime artifacts still deep-import dist/core modules. Align runtime artifacts and tests so installed packages exercise the public SDK surface without losing package functionality."
type: Issue
status: closed
priority: 0
tags[4]: package-first,packages,pm-cli,sdk
created_at: "2026-05-14T05:20:21.502Z"
updated_at: "2026-05-14T05:49:35.175Z"
author: codex-agent
estimated_minutes: 90
acceptance_criteria: First-party package runtime JavaScript artifacts use the public SDK barrel instead of dist/core deep imports; tests fail on stale package runtime artifacts; package-first dogfood and focused package/MCP tests pass; progress and evidence are recorded in pm.
parent: pm-59gj
resolution: "Closed after aligning shipped package runtime JavaScript with the public SDK barrel, adding manifest-declared bundled package aliases, dynamic packages/pm-* discovery, stable extension action IDs, and installed package-command dogfood coverage."
expected_result: "First-party packages remain fully TypeScript-authored, shipped JavaScript avoids private dist/core and dist/types imports, install/catalog/install-all discover package aliases from package manifests, and installed package commands keep working through the SDK surface."
actual_result: "Package JS now imports ../../../../dist/sdk/index.js; runtime guard rejects private dist/core and dist/types imports; beads/todos declare aliases; package catalog/install discover manifest aliases including synthetic pm-custom test fixture; dogfood runs beads import and todos export after install; focused tests, coverage, release gate, Sentry, and telemetry passed."
comments[4]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-05-14T05:20:21.502Z",codex-agent,"Duplicate-check evidence: ran pm context --limit 10, pm search 'package-first SDK packages upgrade extensible' --limit 10, pm search 'MCP dynamic package action dogfood wildcard source refresh' --limit 10, pm list-open --limit 20, and pm list-in-progress --limit 20. Existing pm-hkql closed the TypeScript source cleanup but did not cover stale shipped runtime.js artifacts, so this focused child issue is needed under pm-59gj."
  "2026-05-14T05:30:50.374Z",codex-agent,"Progress: fixed stale first-party package runtime artifacts to import the built public SDK barrel instead of private dist/core internals; added stable package action IDs; added manifest-declared aliases and dynamic bundled package discovery from packages/pm-* manifests; updated dogfood to execute installed beads import and todos export commands. Verification so far: pnpm build passed; pnpm typecheck passed; focused package/MCP suite passed 6 files / 99 tests; pnpm dogfood:package-first passed 37 isolated temp-project commands; pm test pm-2t78 --run --progress passed all 3 linked checks."
  "2026-05-14T05:43:13.771Z",codex-agent,"Final verification: full coverage passed 92 files / 1296 tests with 100% statements/branches/functions/lines. Release gate passed build, typecheck, docs-skills, static quality, coverage, version-policy, secret scan, npx smoke, npm pack dry-run, compatibility check, and required Sentry/telemetry gate. Observability data: Sentry access ok with critical=1 high=3 total=4 under thresholds and 9 ignored known-noise groups; telemetry required mode ok with finish_error_rate_pct=2.46 and failures_without_error_code_rows=0."
  "2026-05-14T05:49:35.175Z",codex-agent,"Post-doc final gate: docs/skills gate passed after documenting pm.aliases. Final release gate rerun passed with telemetry required: build, typecheck, docs-skills, static quality, coverage 92 files / 1296 tests at 100%, version-policy, secret scan, npx smoke, npm pack dry-run, compatibility check, and Sentry/telemetry. Observability final: Sentry critical=1 high=3 total=4 under thresholds with 9 ignored known-noise groups; telemetry finish_error_rate_pct=2.44 and failures_without_error_code_rows=0."
